          The Mudhouse offers a treehouse and 4 mud cottages. The treehouse has a bedroom, a large balcony and a n open-roof bathroom. Witness the beauty of the sun rising through the window of your bedroom or while relaxing with a steaming cup of chai in the living space.
          The property also has a shared kitchen, common dining area and lounge where the guests can have their food or play games.
